nitong mga nakaraan.

01:39:35.500 --> 01:39:38.416
Ang tagal mong sumagot.
I-check mo 'yong link na sinend ko.

01:39:39.166 --> 01:39:42.000
Idolo pa naman 'to ng marami.

01:39:42.083 --> 01:39:43.500
Wala akong ginawa.

01:39:43.583 --> 01:39:44.750
Bigla siyang sumugod

01:39:44.833 --> 01:39:46.166
at sinampal ako,

01:39:46.250 --> 01:39:49.041
