01:39:59.291 --> 01:40:01.583
Para puwedeng gawin sa 'kin 'to
ng asawa mo, Quoc Anh?

01:40:02.333 --> 01:40:04.000
Sobrang napahiya ako.

01:40:04.583 --> 01:40:07.375
Sobrang nakakahiya.

01:40:16.708 --> 01:40:18.000
- Pa-order!
- Sandali lang!

01:40:19.208 --> 01:40:20.291
Ano'ng sa inyo?

01:40:20.375 --> 01:40:21.208
PANCITERIA NI TITA 4

01:40:21.791 --> 01:40:24.208
Uy, siya 'yong babae
sa QA QA Family channel.

01:40:24.291 --> 01:40:25.250
Naalala mo 'yong clip kaninang umaga?

01:40:25.333 --> 01:40:28.250
Uy, di kayo nag-aaway ngayon?

01:40:29.083 --> 01:40:30.083
Nasaan si Quoc Anh?

